# Styling Guidelines

## Critical Styling Rules
1. **Use StyleSheet.create()** for all styles
2. **Use scale() function** for all dimensions, fonts, and spacing
3. **Use color constants** from [src/constants/colors.ts](mdc:src/constants/colors.ts)
4. **Use ThemedText** instead of Text component

## Color Palette
```typescript
import { colors } from '@/src/constants/colors';

// Primary color: #A23021 (dark red/maroon)
// Secondary color: #F5F5F5 (light grey)
// White: #FFFFFF
```

## Responsive Scaling
```typescript
import { scale } from '@/src/constants/responsive';

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  container: {
    padding: scale(20),        // Responsive padding
    fontSize: scale(16),       // Responsive font size
    borderRadius: scale(8),    // Responsive border radius
  },
});
```

## Common Styling Patterns

### Button Styling
```typescript
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  button: {
    backgroundColor: colors.primary,
    paddingHorizontal: scale(20),
    paddingVertical: scale(12),
    borderRadius: scale(8),
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
  buttonText: {
    color: colors.white,
    fontSize: scale(14),
    fontWeight: '600',
  },
});
```

### Card Styling
```typescript
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  card: {
    backgroundColor: colors.white,
    borderRadius: scale(12),
    padding: scale(15),
    shadowColor: '#000',
    shadowOffset: { width: 0, height: 2 },
    shadowOpacity: 0.1,
    shadowRadius: 4,
    elevation: 3,
  },
});
```

### Text Styling
```typescript
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  title: {
    fontSize: scale(18),
    fontWeight: 'bold',
    color: colors.primary,
    marginBottom: scale(8),
  },
  subtitle: {
    fontSize: scale(14),
    color: '#666',
    marginBottom: scale(4),
  },
});
```

## Layout Patterns

### Flexbox Layouts
```typescript
const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  row: {
    flexDirection: 'row',
    alignItems: 'center',
    justifyContent: 'space-between',
  },
  column: {
    flexDirection: 'column',
    justifyContent: 'center',
    alignItems: 'center',
  },
});
```

### ScrollView Styling
```typescript
<ScrollView 
  horizontal 
  showsHorizontalScrollIndicator={false}
  style={styles.cardsContainer}
>
  {/* Content */}
</ScrollView>

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  cardsContainer: {
    marginHorizontal: scale(-20),
    paddingHorizontal: scale(20),
  },
});
```

## ThemedText Usage
```typescript
import { ThemedText } from '@/src/components/themed-text';

<ThemedText style={styles.title}>Title</ThemedText>
<ThemedText style={styles.subtitle}>Subtitle</ThemedText>
```